I have to agree with Bendi and a few others here, everything they have done lately has cut down on the actual challenge of the game.  It is time for some balance, each class has something that makes them needed in groups, and tanks should be able to take ALOT more damage than Monks (now I love my monks don't get me wrong), to me though, that should be common sense.<br>
